@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@conversationId = 1
@messageId = 2

### AI 聊天页面
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai-chat

### 创建会话
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 查询会话列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat/conversations

### 查询会话详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat/conversations/{{conversationId}}

### 发送消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "请整理主动回忆的核心方法和实践建议"
}

### 将 AI 回复保存到待审核资料库
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat/messages/{{messageId}}/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "主动回忆学习方法（AI 生成）"
}
